    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/551ec87e2ef1acb3d072a0212c219453.poster.avif?t=1739896855\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/551ec87e2ef1acb3d072a0212c219453.webm?t=1739896855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/551ec87e2ef1acb3d072a0212c219453.mp4?t=1739896855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>1958年2月17日。索菲在克林顿酒店的工作日开始得像往常一样，直到她打开505房间的门，一个紫色的光从里面射出...</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 'This Bed We Made'</h2><br>'This Bed We Made' 是一个<strong>第三人称叙事式的推理游戏</strong>，为玩家提供3-6小时的游戏体验，可以满足您对他人隐藏生活的好奇心。扮演50年代的好奇女仆索菲，通过酒店客人在旅行中带来的奇怪物品，揭开绑定他们的邪恶之谜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/ba1edaf5061e799d87a5f093e437c672.avif?t=1739896855\" width=623 height=174 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><br>💋 <strong>新黑色调查</strong>：探索克林顿酒店的三个充满氛围的楼层，体验一个关于魅力和谋杀的黑暗、神秘和诱人的故事；<br><br>💋 <strong>好奇心驱动的调查</strong>：在360度的视角中查看物品，解决难题，探索其他人的(不是那么)隐藏的生活；<br><br>💋 <strong>亲密的关系</strong>：与酒店的员工和客人建立亲密的关系，选择冒险的贝特还是学者安德鲁；<br><br>💋 <strong>真实的结局</strong>：你的每一步，你打开的每一扇门都可能改变故事的走向... 包括你如何打扫房间！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/80ec6d4a5a5fd4af35915ff83e3510a5.poster.avif?t=1739896855\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/80ec6d4a5a5fd4af35915ff83e3510a5.webm?t=1739896855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243850/extras/80ec6d4a5a5fd4af35915ff83e3510a5.mp4?t=1739896855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
